iving area significantly with a useful rooftop terrace. Inside, it features a space-saving layout that's packed with storage and can sleep up to five people at a squeeze.</p><p><a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tiny-houses/white-pine-backcountry-tiny-homes/\">Continue Reading</a></p><p><b>Category:</b> <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tiny-houses/\">Tiny Houses</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/outdoors/\">Outdoors</a></p><p><b>Tags:</b> <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/micro-housing/\" rel=\"tag\">Micro-House</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/home/\" rel=\"tag\">Home</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/tiny-footprint/\" rel=\"tag\">Tiny Footprint</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/danish-mirror-house/21118/\" rel=\"tag\">House</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/building+and+construction/\" rel=\"tag\">Building and Construction</a></p>",
